Interface TextAction<R>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - the type of the result of the action
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClickAction<R>, ClickAction.ChangePage, ClickAction.OpenUrl, ClickAction.RunCommand, ClickAction.SuggestCommand, HoverAction<R>, HoverAction.ShowAchievement, HoverAction.ShowEntity, HoverAction.ShowItem, HoverAction.ShowText, ShiftClickAction<R>, ShiftClickAction.InsertText

    public interface TextAction<R>
    Represents an action happening as a response to an event on a Message .
